title: Hour 3 - Doug Gottlieb and Michael Wilbon (04-30-20)
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Doug Gottlieb and Michael Wilbon (04-30-20)
description:
Doug Gottlieb discusses high school players that will go straight to the NBA G League. Doug also talks about the percentage of players that should not go to the NBA G League. Michael Wilbon says that the Green Bay Packers draft pick was an act of unbelievable arrogance. Michael says he was only kidding when he said Aaron Rodgers will be in a Bears uniform in the near future.
